# Deploy + MCP

## Targets

| Layer | Host | Root / note |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Frontend | Vercel | Root Directory = `frontend` |
| Backend | Render | `render.yaml` → `rootDir: backend` + Postgres |

## Env

- FE: `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=<Render URL>`
- BE: `DATABASE_URL`, `JWT_SECRET`, `CORS_ORIGINS=<Vercel URL>`, `TRUST_PROXY=true`, `APP_ENV=production`

## MCP order

1. Render MCP — API + DB blueprint / env / logs  
2. Vercel MCP — FE deploy + env  
3. Set `CORS_ORIGINS` to the live Vercel origin  
4. MF Academy MCP — delivery / mentor flow  

Update README live URLs only after both sides are actually live.
